OL,3,CBotched BBLs: Glasgow bans company and
OL,4,Cpractitioner after woman hospitalised
OL,6,FAn ITV investigation has found that an
OL,7,Faesthetics practitioner and two
OL,8,Fcompanies have been banned from
OL,9,Fcarrying out Brazilian Butt Lifts in
OL,10,FGlasgow, after a woman was left
OL,11,Fneeding hospital treatment
OL,13,FTwo companies and an aesthetics
OL,14,Fpractitioner have been banned from
OL,15,Fcarrying out Brazilian Butt Lifts in
OL,16,FGlasgow after a woman was taken to
OL,17,Fhospital following a BBL procedure.
