OL,6,F"People need to be extremely careful
OL,7,Fwhen considering undergoing cosmetic
OL,8,Fprocedures. If they go wrong - the
OL,9,Fconsequences can be painful,
OL,10,Fdisfiguring and require emergency
OL,11,Fmedical treatment.
OL,13,F"Our Environmental Health officers are
OL,14,Falso carrying out inspections of
OL,15,Faesthetic clinics in the city to help
OL,16,Fsafeguard the public and will continue
OL,17,Fto take enforcement action when
OL,18,Frequired."
